{{define "fresh-evidence-checklist"}}- [ ] Current `run_version` matches the latest execution run for this change.
- [ ] Every pass claim cites a command or transcript captured after the latest relevant code change.
- [ ] Evidence references, timestamps, and reports come from the same freshness window.
- [ ] Reused earlier proof is called out by prior `run_version`; it is never presented as fresh evidence.
{{end}}

{{define "fresh-evidence-minimum-record"}}- current `run_version`
- reproducible command or transcript reference
- timestamp from the same freshness window
- blocker when proof is stale or missing (`stale_verification_evidence` / `missing_fresh_run`)
{{end}}
